{"image_id": "PMC4965068_3", "image_size": [773, 1000], "ocr": [{"text": "Heparanase in the Ischemia/Reperfusion-Induced EMT", "bbox": [486.0, 49.0, 727.3, 60.5]}, {"text": "Fig 1. Schematic representation of in vitro experimental design. Serum starved HK-2 cells were exposed to 24 h of hypoxia and subsequently", "bbox": [93.6, 583.0, 726.7, 595.6]}, {"text": "to reoxygenation (6 h for gene expression and 24 h for protein expression analysis). Cells were also treated or not with 200 μg/ml SST0001 (red", "bbox": [93.6, 595.4, 714.4, 607.0]}, {"text": "balls) before the hypoxia (point #4; herein after referred to as H/R1) and before reoxygenation (point #5; herein after called H/R2). Control cells", "bbox": [93.6, 607.5, 709.6, 619.0]}, {"text": "were cultured in normoxic conditions with or without SST0001 (points #1 and 2).", "bbox": [93.6, 619.4, 439.7, 631.0]}, {"text": "doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0160074.g001", "bbox": [93.6, 639.1, 236.7, 650.5]}, {"text": "Table 1. Primers sequence list.", "bbox": [45.5, 683.5, 191.2, 695.3]}, {"text": "Gene Forward 5’-3’ Reverse 5’-3’", "bbox": [113.3, 702.2, 628.8, 714.1]}, {"text": "Human", "bbox": [108.8, 718.6, 142.8, 730.5]}, {"text": "GAPDH ACACCCACTCCTCCACCTTT TCCACCACCCTGTTGCTGTA", "bbox": [107.9, 734.7, 658.0, 746.8]}, {"text": "HPSE ATTTGAATGGACGGACTGC GTTTCTCCTAACCAGACCTTC", "bbox": [112.1, 750.5, 661.0, 762.6]}, {"text": "α-SMA GAAGAAGAGGACAGCACTG TCCCATTCCCACCATCAC", "bbox": [110.4, 766.2, 652.0, 778.3]}, {"text": "FN GTGTGTTGGGAATGGTCGTG GACGCTTGTGGAATGTGTCG", "bbox": [119.1, 782.0, 658.0, 794.1]}, {"text": "Mouse", "bbox": [109.9, 797.5, 141.6, 809.4]}, {"text": "GAPDH GGCAAATTCAACGGCACAGT GTCTCGCTCCTGGAAGATGG", "bbox": [107.9, 813.6, 658.0, 825.7]}, {"text": "HPSE CAAGAACAGCACCTACTCAAG AGCAGTAGTCAAGGAGAAGC", "bbox": [112.1, 829.4, 658.0, 841.5]}, {"text": "α-SMA TGCTGGACTCTGGAGATGGT ACGAAGGAATAGCCACGCTC", "bbox": [110.4, 845.2, 658.0, 857.3]}, {"text": "VIM TCCAGAGAGAGGAAGCCGAA AAGGTCAAGACGTGCCAGAG", "bbox": [116.